name: AGENT_STATE_LICENSE_NUMS
description: The table that stores information for State License Numbers (SLNs). Including the SLN, State, Eff date, Term Date.

columns.name: AGENT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the agent record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: LICENSE_EFF_DATE
columns.description: Agent State License Number Effective Date

columns.name: LICENSE_TERM_DATE
columns.description: Agent's State License Number Termination Date
